:::Cyclonus/Scourge:::

::Cyclonus and Scourge were flying around the world searching for Decepticons 
they stop and land to rest awhile::
Scourge: Ughh, we've flown around this entire planet and we havent found a 
trace of Decepticons.
Cyclonus: We should keep searching, theres gotta be a base or something.
::They keep walking and finally sense some Decepticon energy signatures in a 
nearby base::
Scourge: Jackpot!
Cyclonus: I hated him.
Scourge: No, i mean Jackpot! We found a Decepticon base!
Cyclonus: oh.
::Cyclonus opens up a comm to the base::
Cyclonus: You are Decepticons, right? We would like to join you.
Scourge: This is Cyclonus and Scourge, by the way.
